Invocation Name: supernatural quotes
des:
Start your day with an inspirational list of quotes. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. 
You can make a game of it by guessing who said it before Alexa tells you.
These quotes will be updated periodically. If you think of one that should be included or if I've made a mistake in the wording, speaker or episode number, tweet me @eccentrician . I'm only human... to forgive divine.
This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
